Alien-nghttp2

Alien::nghttp2 provides the nghttp2 HTTP/2 C library to Perl
distributions via Alien::Base. It can either use an existing system
installation or build nghttp2 from source when needed.

Installation

    cpanm Alien::nghttp2

Or from a checkout:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

The module exposes standard Alien::Base methods such as `cflags`,
`libs`, and `dynamic_libs` for consumers that need to compile or link
against nghttp2.

See `lib/Alien/nghttp2.pm` for API details and usage examples.
